#User Guide

##How to Run the Project

1. Run DatabaseSetup.java
   - This will create the database and tables
   - It will also insert sample data

2. Run PetAdoptionApp.java
   - This will open the menu system

##Menu Options

1. View available pets
   - Displays pets with status "Available"

2. Submit adoption application
   - Enter adopter ID and pet ID
   - Application will be saved in database

3. View adoption applications
   - Displays all applications with adopter name and pet name

4. Exit
   - Closes the program

##Notes
- The database file is created automatically(petadoption.db)
- Running the setup multiple times will not cause errors
